'''Medical Director of the Year Award'''

The Medical Director of the Year Award (MDOY) is given annually by the AMDA Foundation, an affiliate of [[AMDA – Dedicated to Long Term Care Medicine]] (AMDA). The MDOY Award recognizes [[medical directors]] with exceptional leadership and commitment to quality patient care.<ref>{{cite web|title=Medical Director of the Year Award|url=http://www.amda.com/awards/mdoty.cfm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061018071124/http://www.amda.com/awards/mdoty.cfm|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2006-10-18}}</ref> [[Nominations]] are accepted annually and reviewed by a Selection Committee. Recipients are awarded at AMDA’s annual symposium, Long Term Care Medicine.

Past Recipients of the Medical Director of the Year Award

• 2012 Noel DeBacker, MD, CMD <ref>{{cite web|last=Kaldy|first=Joanne|title=AMDA’s 2012 Medical Director of the Year Embraces Change|url=http://www.caringfortheages.com/news/more-top-news/single-view/amdas-2012-medical-director-of-the-year-embraces-change/036a5504009626bdfb1f1bf6e7e83b78.html|work=Caring for the Ages|publisher=Elsevier|accessdate=3/08/12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130119124712/http://www.caringfortheages.com/news/more-top-news/single-view/amdas-2012-medical-director-of-the-year-embraces-change/036a5504009626bdfb1f1bf6e7e83b78.html|archivedate=2013-01-19|df=}}</ref>

• 2011 Sabine von Preyss-Friedman, MD, CMD <ref>{{cite web|title=AMDA Names Medical Director of the Year|url=http://long-term-care.advanceweb.com/News/Product-Releases/AMDA-Names-Medical-Director-of-the-Year.aspx|work=Advances for Long Term Care Management|publisher=Merion Matters}}</ref>

• 2010 Robert Schreiber, MD, CMD <ref>{{cite web|last=Hess|first=Susan|title=Seniorlink Commends Dr. Robert Schreiber and Dr. James Ellison for Their Contribution to Geriatric Medicine and Recent Awards of Excellence|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100325006457/en/Seniorlink-Commends-Dr.-Robert-Schreiber-Dr.-James|work=Seniorlink, Inc.|publisher=BusinessWire}}</ref>

